node.text: Couldn’t ask for a better way to wake up🧡 Cheers to 24🥂 feeling so loved today and every other day by all you guys and especially my amazing husband☺️ 23 was a good one… Got married, bought our second house, traveled a ton, grew our businesses, met new people and was challenged in ways like never before with Josh’s  accident! Excited for what’s to come in my 24th year🥰 Thank you everyone for all your bday wishes!
